extends baseEmail

block content
  table(width="100%" border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0")
    tr
      td(style="padding-bottom: 24px;")
        h2(style="color: #B18958; margin: 0 0 24px; font-size: 20px;") Welcome to the EulaIQ Beta Program!
    tr
      td(style="padding-bottom: 16px;")
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") Hello #{firstName},
    tr
      td(style="padding-bottom: 24px;")
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") 
          | Thank you for joining our exclusive beta program! You're among the first to experience EulaIQ's innovative approach to medical education.
    tr
      td(style="padding: 16px; background-color: #F5F7FA; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 24px;")
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") 
          strong As a beta tester, you'll receive:
          ul(style="margin-top: 8px; padding-left: 20px;")
            li(style="margin-bottom: 8px;") 2 months of free access when we fully launch
            li(style="margin-bottom: 8px;") Early access to new features before public release
            li(style="margin-bottom: 8px;") Direct channel to our development team for feedback
    tr
      td(style="padding-bottom: 24px; padding-top: 16px;")
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") 
          | Your download should begin automatically. If not, please click the download button below:
    tr
      td(align="center" style="padding-bottom: 32px;")
        a(href=url style="background-color: #B18958; color: #FFFFFF; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 4px; display: inline-block;") Download EulaIQ App
    tr
      td(style="padding-bottom: 24px;")
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") 
          | We value your feedback and suggestions as we continue to improve EulaIQ. Please don't hesitate to reach out with any questions or comments.
    tr
      td(style="padding: 24px; background-color: #F5F7FA; border-radius: 8px;")
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0 0 12px; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") 
          strong Need help or have feedback?
        p(style="color: #2D2D2D; margin: 0; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5;") 
          | Contact our support team at 
          a(href="mailto:support@eulaiq.com" style="color: #B18958; text-decoration: none;") support@eulaiq.com
